  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK467">
<l>eṇṇit tuṇika karuman tuṇintapi</l>
<l>ṉeṇṇuva meṉpa tiḻukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Consider, and then undertake a matter; after having undertaken it, to say "We will consider," is folly.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
